block content
  body
    .navbar
      a(href='/home' id = 'Home') Jio
      a(href='/files/JioCalderonResume.pdf' id = 'Resume') Resume
      a(href='/about' id = 'About') About
      a(href='/login' id = 'Login') Login
      a(href='/blog' id = 'Blog') Blog
      a(href='https://github.com/J10calderon' id = 'Github') Github
      a(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/jio-calderon-2782b8156/' id = 'Linkedin') LinkedIn



  head
    title Express authentication example
  body
    h1 Sign-in to this Express authentication example
    p Use <i>user</i> for the username and <i>pass</i> for the password.
    form(method='post', action = '/login')
      p
        label(for='username') Username
        input(type='text', name='username')
      p
        label(for='password') Password
        input(type='password', name='password')
      input(type='submit')


    form(method='get', action = '/logout')
      input(type='submit')
      
    - each message in flash
      h4(style="color: orange;") #{message}